    "155885767": {
      "title": "Social and organisational renorming of education",
      "abstract": "This section focuses on the steps taken by the State Governments of Australia, for reshaping and restructuring the education system. It also provides an insight into the policy interventions of the Victorian education system in secondary schools and Institute of Technical and Further Education (TAFE)."
    }
